<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"


    android:id="@+id/ScrollView01"

    android:fillViewport="false">

    <LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
        xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools" android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent" android:paddingLeft="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
        android:paddingTop="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:paddingBottom="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:background="@drawable/bg6"
        tools:context="com.example.sudhanshumishra.astrovision.Virgo"
        android:orientation="vertical"
        >


        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="380dp"
            android:layout_height="1250dp"
            android:weightSum="1"
            android:orientation="vertical"
            >

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="350dp"
                android:layout_height="110dp"
                android:text="VIRGO"
                android:textSize="80dp"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textAlignment="center"
                />

            <ImageView
                android:layout_width="310dp"
                android:layout_height="250dp"
                android:background="@drawable/virgo" />


            <HorizontalScrollView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                >

                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="350dp"
                    android:layout_height="480dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                    android:textColor="#33FF33"
                    android:inputType="textMultiLine"
                    android:text="Strength\n
- Analytical\n
- Observant\n
- Helpful\n
- Reliable\n
- Precise\n\n

Weakness:\n
- Skeptical\n
- Fussy\n
- Inflexible\n
- Cold\n
- Interfering\n\n

Virgo is a very independent zodiac sign. They are fully able\n
to put their intelligence to use and get things done for themselves.\n
It is possible however that their narrow mindedness causes their\n
creativity to suffer and they may lead regular routine lives.They\n
may dwell too much on the past and over complicate things and this\n
may limit their ability to move forward and confuse themselves.\n
In conclusion,Virgos are able to be independent but the less evolved\n
types will have difficult if someone is not there helping them to\n
achieve more and not be so critical of themselves.\n
"    />

            </HorizontalScrollView>
            <TextView
                android:layout_width="350dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:id="@+id/tv_luck"
                android:textColor="#33FF33"
                />

            <EditText
                android:layout_width="320dp"
                android:layout_height="150dp"
                android:background="#FAD7A0"
                android:textColorHint="#A569BD"
                android:id="@id/edt_msg"
                />
            <Button
                android:layout_width="90dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="140dp"
                android:text="call"
                android:onClick="callme"
                />
            <Button
                android:layout_width="90dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="140dp"
                android:text="sms"
                android:onClick="send"
                />
        </LinearLayout>


        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="350dp"
            android:layout_height="60dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="30dp"
            >

            <Button
                android:layout_width="120dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:text="Sign Out"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textSize="10dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="120dp"
                android:onClick="signout"
                />
        </LinearLayout>
    </LinearLayout>


</ScrollView>
